5.1.1 As an integral part of the agreement, you are required to maintain ownership and uninterrupted operation of The Original Soupman businesses, beyond those you initially hold, as outlined on Attachment E (the "Expansion Quota"). However, we will refrain from granting other franchises or establishing our own Unit Franchises within the Master Territory for the duration of this Agreement, unless you successfully meet the Expansion Quota. Should you fail to meet the Expansion Quota, we retain the discretionary right to:

a) Extend your exclusive privilege to market and sell Unit Franchises in the Master Territory to additional franchisees;
b) Establish more Master Franchises within your allocated territory;
c) Operate our own units within your Master Territory; or
d) Terminate this Agreement.

In essence, the onus lies with you to maintain the agreed expansion pace, and we will only take actions outlined above if necessary due to non-compliance with the Expansion Quota.
